trans-unit.source: Welcome to the SimpleTaskManager for OpenStreetMap

Changes in 1.1.0: New features:
Internationalization:
Translation of STM into Chinese, German and Japanese Selection dialog to change the language Selected language stored in the browsers local storage
Button to open task in iD Button to directly set a task as 'done' Longer token validity (your login is now valid for one week) Check GeoJSON format of each new task
Bug fixes:
Missing feedback on overpass error Reconnect on broken websocket connection
Minor changes:
Zoom to selected task when not visible on the screen Progress percentage in project list Automatic names of tasks (the numbers of unnamed now start at 1 in each new project)
Internals:
Store project-ID in task database table Create project and tasks within one HTTP request Introduce the context to add a logging trace-ID Better server side logging Reconnect to database after connection failure Source maps in karma tests

trans-unit.source: Upload a GPX, OSM or GeoJSON file, which contains polygons. Each polygon will result in a single task.
